thread.title: BRIEF-Ctac FY Net Result Up At 2.8‍​ Million Euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Ctac FY Net Result Up At 2.8‍​ Million Euros
text:
March 9 (Reuters) - CTAC NV:
* Q4 NET TURNOVER EUR 22.1 MILLION VERSUS EUR 22.8 MILLION YEAR AGO
* EXPECTED HIGHER NET RESULT IN 2018 COMPARED TO 2017 * FY NET RESULT EUR 2.8‍​ MILLION VERSUS EUR 2.6 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY EBITDA RISES BY 11.3% TO EUR 4.7 MILLION‍​ * WE EXPECT TO REALISE A HIGHER RESULT IN 2018 COMPARED TO 2017‍​
* Q4 OPERATING RESULT EUR 1.6‍​ MILLION VERSUS EUR 1.1 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q4 NET RESULT EUR 1.3 ‍​ MILLION VERSUS EUR 1.3 MILLION YEAR AGO Source text : bit.ly/2G9WKwH Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
